WEBVTT

00:04:58.960 --> 00:05:02.896
made the debt-to-GDP ratio
fall down to about 30 percent,

00:05:02.920 --> 00:05:06.816
and there was enough resources
to try and reinvest.

00:05:06.840 --> 00:05:09.296
The third thing was
loss-making enterprises.

00:05:09.320 --> 00:05:11.376
Governments were involved in business

00:05:11.400 --> 00:05:13.656
which they had no business being in.

00:05:13.680 --> 00:05:16.776
And they were running businesses,
they were making losses.

00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:19.536
So some of these enterprises
were restructured,

00:05:19.560 --> 00:05:21.976
commercialized, privatized or closed,

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:25.200
and they became
less of a burden on government.

00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:28.480
The fourth thing
